      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software QA documentation covers version control, regression testing, and release notes for all FEA codes used (Ansys Mechanical 2022R2, FDA in-house solver v4.1).",
      "rationale": "All three FEA codes used in the ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes proprietary) maintain formal version-controlled repositories with regression test suites covering >200 benchmark cases. Release notes and change logs reviewed. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2 for a medium-risk COU."
